dataIdInfo.idPurp: This table provides permissible use and density information for the adopted Area Plans, Community Plans, and Plan Area Statements in the Tahoe Basin.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Attribute Table fields:

Zoning_ID: Zoning code

Category: Use category

Subcategory: Use Subcategory

Use: Use Type

Use_Status: Allowable or Special Use status

Density: Density number

Unit: Density unit

Notes: Extra information

The data is in no way an exhaustive list of the implementing regulations of the area plans, community plans, and plan area statements. Please refer to specific local plans for more detailed information on zoning regulations and permissible uses within the Tahoe Basin.

Much of the TRPA GIS data is parcel based and therefore attribute data for such features are constantly changing. We recognize these errors and make an effort to correct them as they are discovered.
